data.description: Welcome to this cozy 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom brick house built in 2021. It features LVP floors throughout the living area (YES, NO CARPET IN THE LIVING ROOM!), an open concept layout, and a fenced-in backyard. The kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, and the refrigerator conveys as is with the house. Conveniently located near shopping centers and the new Semmes Publix, this home offers modern comfort in a prime location. Schedule a viewing today!
